Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.98,0:00:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Police Dept. Interrogation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stay silent, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4:00pm today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:39.31,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Togashi Fumitaka (32)\NEx-con
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:37.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This man - Togashi Fumitaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:41.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Will be sent to the prosecutor as a murder suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:43.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They call it a prosecutor's takeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything started yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, be sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro is in the interrogation room...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's fighting hard for the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday Afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musashino Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.55,0:03:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been keeping at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi Fumitaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a murderer who was arrested by\NUncle while he was still a police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today, he went on parole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(210,0)}Hakamada Tsuneo (34)\NEx-con
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Throw it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a small celebration, I've already made a reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to treat you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hakamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, the murder happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 10:00 PM last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A parole officer living at 4th Street in Beika City,\N55-year-old Sakuraba Takehiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was found murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A former convict released on parole\Nyesterday from Musashino Prison...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One which Officer Sakuraba\NTakehiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had supervised...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi Fumitaka, age 32, has been\Narrested in connection with the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today 10:05 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:07.40,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu Norio (52)\N{\fs12}Beika Police First Division Detective
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Keeping your mouth shut won't save you, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri is waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi was the one you arrested all that time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He accidentally killed his victim in a dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His attorney claimed it was self defense, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He behaved violently in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And had a long rap sheet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which earned him a thirteen year jail sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, this guy was actually a nice guy at heart and loved his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While serving his time, he changed and become a model inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He murdered again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his first night of parole?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It goes to show that people can't change easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will begin the prosecutor's takeover paperwork as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you wait just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But forget about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're only a private detective now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no call for outsiders to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kasamatsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, proceed with your paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the prosecutor's takeover will\Ncommence as planned - at 4:00pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, we'll be on break until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi will remain in custody in the interrogation room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What nonsense is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't some sort of joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will pass the word to your supervisor myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always appreciated your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I repeat:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our break ends at 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle got special permission to continue interrogating Togashi, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stay silent, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's wounds are mostly on the right side of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop that, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just snoop around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean the culprit held the weapon in their left hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It matches the witness testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not left-handed, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there are wounds that aren't on the left side as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've been wrestling with the\Nvictim and switched to another hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's certainly a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To confirm that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, where's the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be bad if you got lost, so I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the interrogation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're taking a lunch break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:23.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go to the crime scene now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, about Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's telling me to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he said there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} went home already too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, everybody's in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle forgot to tell you something so he wants me to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's not much time left until the takeover, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember, Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After six months of time served, you sent me a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you had been spending your days\Nfeeling remorse and bettering yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you'd walk away clean and take care of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You regained your footing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I had never thought being a\Npolice detective could be so rewarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the happiest one must've been your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she doing all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Togashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch anything on your own, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Reconstruct the crime scene according to witness testimony."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even requested that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:10:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was seen through this window, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The witness is that lady over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are the pools of blood so far apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These shiny shards are from that mirror, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the mirror from that cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like it was smashed during the\Nstruggle between the culprit and the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the weapon dropped here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fingerprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There weren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was wiped clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only the weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sliding screens and places the\Nculprit most likely touched were all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's prints aren't there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kitchen, bathroom, bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the victim's everyday fingerprints were wiped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did they have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:58.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, when and where was Togashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 10:30 last night, in Beika Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the time when the murder was witnessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes before that, around 10:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Park: from here to there would take\N7 or 8 minutes, even if you were running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the crime, they only had a few\Nminutes to tamper with the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could they have wiped them before the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, they did it while the crime was ongoing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be, another person was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is quite likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time of arrest, Togashi was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, they split up and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only been one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we can find more witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I arrested you at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:12:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was because your friend was beaten up\Nby gangsters, but you tried to fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be, you're helping someone out again this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, another person was involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me right now, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pause it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, about the thing Uncle Kogoro forgot to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I totally forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about the witness testimony reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted you to do it for both sides - for\Nthe crime scene and where the witness was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.01,0:13:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you witnessed the crime through these windows\Nand into that house's window, right Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:22.28,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}Yoshizawa Kane (75)\NWitness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's right, it was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thunder and lightning, and then there was a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without thinking, I looked out the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though I couldn't see his face, our eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He faced the window and threw the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was not near the window,\Nbut was instead in front of the cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you saw it wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my eyes are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My eyesight hasn't changed since I was 30 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see anything after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although, there were several more lightning strikes afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was actually like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that's the case, we may have come to a surprising truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.29,0:14:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Togashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat thhheee...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, just sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Detective Takagi wanted to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To suddenly make a funny sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, after that he usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something more to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He usually does this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, this is that famous Sleeping Kogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the prosecutor's takeover at 4:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to reveal every bit of truth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you have at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this "something more" about the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that murder crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was actually someone else present...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which adds something more to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.58,0:15:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi is currently investigating this man's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you telling us that this man is our real culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a witness who testified that she saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't see his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how would you explain all of the blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the forensics, the blood on him matches the victim's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a pity, but we have a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like the victim was a so-called malicious parole officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He made a lot of empty promises, such as\Nassuring there would be no prosecution...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he took advantage of suspects' families\Nto squeeze out large sums of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A year and a half ago, your mother suffered\Nfrom his pressure and died of illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's just as we thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that motive, one more man fits in as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under the same pressure, his wife and son committed suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is the man caught on tape by a convenience store camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakamada Tsuneo, 34 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, he went on parole along with Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, Hakamada is left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would also explain the concentrated\Namount of wounds on the right side of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recall the witness reporting the culprit\Nholding the weapon in his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy from Musashino Prison who went on parole yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakamada Tsuneo, check his whereabouts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy... Hakamada had nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakamada turned himself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to my wife and son's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I planned to turn myself in after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it's true you committed the crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We became pals while in the slammer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when he discovered my plan to murder Sakuraba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I proceeded ahead, despite Togashi's warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally did the deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Togashi arrived at the scene, completely stunned...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he told me, "I'll take care of the fingerprints, so flee at once!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without thinking, I fled the scene just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was caught as a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, after letting Hakamada go,\Nhe didn't know what had been touched...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a result, he wiped off even\Nthe victim's everyday fingerprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to hand it to you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, an innocent person wasn't used as a scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time was Hakamada caught on tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 10:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is the exact time Yoshizawa Kane{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} witnessed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would mean Hakamada was at two\Ndifferent places at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakamada had blood on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which put him on the scene, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time the witness saw the crime scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did the witness say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:43.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though I couldn't see his face, our eyes met.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He faced the witness and threw the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The weapon was not near the window, but was near\Nthe cabinet, among the shattered mirror shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meaning, the culprit didn't face the witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead faced the mirror and threw the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, what the witness saw was a reflection of the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, what we thought was the left\Nhand of the culprit holding a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was actually his right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.02,0:20:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was shocked by the reflection of the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he immediately threw his weapon into the mirror, breaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the culprit who was seen was right-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the culprit who fled previously was left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying the victim was murdered twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is only one imaginable scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim who was thought to be dead came to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was finished off by another culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:56.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi... it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hakamada and my families had to suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The long day in the interrogation room finally came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Next Day 9:00 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Togashi Fumitaka Being Sent to the Prosecutor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:44.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,While I was sitting in that interrogation room yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:48.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I wish you had been the one to tell me the truth, Togashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you couldn't tell an old detective like\Nme who wasn't even aware your mother had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.89,0:22:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was scared, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, because of you, I didn't have to make Hakamada my scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems like I lost my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, give Eri a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't mean for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want her to represent Togashi, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But let's get together for lunch while we're at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that woman really insists...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess wasting some time on that wouldn't be too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Wasting some time" and "wouldn't be too bad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you keep that up...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What just popped out!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, why did you sprain your ankle, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think I would tell you such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haruna{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of that girl now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.87,0:24:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:32.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's the Kinosaki hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:36.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.58,0:24:33.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Then, to the hot spring I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.86,0:24:34.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Inspector, you're staying home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.83,0:24:35.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What!?
